--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Man Page
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Man page source for pal is at:

	./doc/pal.1

This can be read with:

	$ nroff -man ./doc.pal.1 | less

or
	$ make man

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Documentation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LaTeX source for full documentation can be found at

	./doc/pal.tex

with a compiled PDF of the document at

	./doc/pal.pdf
